Tampaknya pedagang sutra, Jang Il Soo,

330
00:19:09,850 --> 00:19:12,520
menyuap dia sesuai yang disuruh oleh para atasan.

331
00:19:12,859 --> 00:19:14,560
Pedagang yang tidak berkuasa bisa apa?

332
00:19:15,090 --> 00:19:16,859
Menghasut kesaksian palsu dan penyuapan.

333
00:19:18,500 --> 00:19:20,100
Akan sulit baginya untuk lolos dari ini.

334
00:19:20,929 --> 00:19:22,770
Dia naif.

335
00:19:22,770 --> 00:19:25,369
Bisa-bisanya dia memercayai bangsawan dan bekerja sama?

336
00:19:35,679 --> 00:19:37,550
Di mana dia?

337
00:19:41,379 --> 00:19:42,389
Tuan.

338
00:19:43,590 --> 00:19:44,590
Astaga.

339
00:19:45,060 --> 00:19:47,619
Anda tidak apa-apa, Tuan?

340
00:19:47,619 --> 00:19:48,790
Anda di sini.

341
00:19:49,689 --> 00:19:50,689
Pangeran Yeoning.

342
00:19:53,929 --> 00:19:54,959
Rupanya kamu.

343
00:19:58,770 --> 00:20:01,040
Kasihan sekali kamu memiliki

344
00:20:02,270 --> 00:20:03,439
